 {ok}←{type}Click id;b;ok;time;reTry
 ⍝ Click on an element, by default identified by id. See "Find" for options
 'type'DefaultTo'Id'
 ok←reTry←0
 :Repeat
     :Trap 90
         b←type Find id
         b.Click
         ok←1
     :Else
         reTry+←1
         ⎕DL 1
     :EndTrap
 :Until ok∨reTry>3
 ('Control "',id,'" not found')⎕SIGNAL(0≡b)/11
